FSG is a foundation registered in Spain and has no members. &#xd;
&#xd;
EURoma Network (of which FSG is the Technical Secretariat), brings together public authorities responsible for Roma policies (National Roma Contact Points) and those responsible for ESI Funds (Managing Authorities, Intermediate Bodies/Implementing Authorities or other general structures for the management of these funds) from 15 EU Member States (see www.euromanet.eu/about-us/who-is-who/)
